fields.name: Vacuum Cleaning
fields.description: We use powerful dry vacuuming to suck dirt and dust from Seats, Carpets, Boot, Floor Matts, and rear Speaker Tray together with light brushing for the best output in the least time.

fields.name: Intensive Classic Interior Cleaning
fields.description: Complete dry cleaning of an interior including seats (carpet/leather), roof, mats, and boot, Dressings to all vinyl, plastic, rubber giving your car spotless, shiny, glossy interior.

fields.name: Intensive Premium Interior Cleaning
fields.description: Complete dry cleaning of an interior including seats (carpet/leather), roof, mats, and boot, Dressings to all vinyl, plastic, rubber giving your car spotless, shiny, glossy interior.

fields.name: Quick Wash

fields.name: Wax Rubbing

fields.name: Teflon Coating
fields.description: Our PTFE-based Polymer paint sealant creates a slippery, slick barrier that protects the paint finishes, reduces fading & oxidation of the paint. It repels dirt & grime, accelerates water run-off to reduce spotting, smoothness weathered surface, and removes scratches giving depth to the paint.
